### Local-dev Spring profile — must NOT be committed (carries the legacy
### smartbiomed/smartbiomed credential for backwards-compatibility). The
### committed `application-dev.properties.example` is the template a new
### developer should copy to `application-dev.properties` after rotation.
src/main/resources/application-dev.properties
src/main/resources/application-local.properties
